+### Pages
+
+| Page ID | Title | Directory |
+|---------|-------|-----------|
+| `clicks` | Clicks | `pages/clicks` |
+
+The **Clicks** page (`/pages/clicks/`) renders the click forest as an interactive tree view. Features:
+- Persistent right-hand detail pane showing the selected click's fields, children, links, and lifecycle actions
+- Status-filter buttons prune non-matching nodes and their subtrees (All / live / parked / concluded / dropped)
+- All nodes expanded by default; collapse/expand individual subtrees
+- CSS badge status indicators matching the shared Oculus badge vocabulary
+- Focus button on each node scopes the tree to that subtree (`?root=<id>`); breadcrumb navigation with "Show all"
+- Toggleable inline create-click form at the top of the tree
+- Deep-link support: `?click=<id>` auto-opens that click's detail pane; `?root=<id>` scopes the tree
+- Link navigation dispatches by ID prefix: `c-…` opens the click detail in-page; `w-…` navigates to the Writs page
+- Link target metadata lazily fetched and displayed alongside each link ID
+- Park / Resume / Conclude / Drop lifecycle actions in the detail pane (conclude/drop require a non-empty conclusion)
+
